微软推出2.7B参数语言模型Phi-2 https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/2023/12/13/microsoft-unveils-2-7b-parameter-language-model-phi-2/ https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/2023/12/13/microsoft-unveils-2-7b-parameter-language-model-phi-2/#respondRyan Daws Wed, 13 Dec 2023 16:59:31 +0000 Artificial IntelligenceCompaniesDevelopmentMicrosoftaiartificial intelligencebenchmarkcomparisonlanguage modelmicrosoftModelphi 2phi-2 https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/?p=14069 <p>微软的27亿参数模型Phi-2展示了出色的推理和语言理解能力，为参数少于130亿的基础语言模型树立了新的性能标准。 Phi-2 建立在其前身 Phi-1 和 Phi-1.5 的成功基础上，通过模型匹配或超越高达 25 倍的模型——这要归功于模型缩放方面的创新和<a class="excerpt-read-more" href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/2023/12/13/microsoft-unveils-2-7b-parameter-language-model-phi-2/" title="Read微软推出2.7B参数语言模型Phi-2">... 阅读更多 ”</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/2023/12/13/microsoft-unveils-2-7b-parameter-language-model-phi-2/">微软推出 2.7B 参数语言模型 Phi-2 的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com">AI News</a>上。</p> ; 
<p>微软的27亿参数模型<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/blog/phi-2-the-surprising-power-of-small-language-models/">Phi-2</a>展示了出色的推理和语言理解能力，为参数少于130亿的基础语言模型树立了新的性能标准。</p><p> Phi-2 建立在其前身 Phi-1 和 Phi-1.5 的成功基础上，通过模型扩展和训练数据管理方面的创新，匹配或超越了高达 25 倍的模型。</p><p> Phi-2 的紧凑尺寸使其成为研究人员的理想游乐场，有助于探索机械可解释性、安全性改进以及跨各种任务的微调实验。</p><p> Phi-2 的成就基于两个关键方面：</p><ul><li><strong>训练数据质量：</strong>微软强调训练数据质量在模型性能中的关键作用。 Phi-2 利用“教科书质量”的数据，专注于旨在传授常识推理和一般知识的合成数据集。训练语料库通过精心挑选的网络数据进行扩充，并根据教育价值和内容质量进行过滤。</li></ul><ul><li><strong>创新的扩展技术：</strong> Microsoft 采用创新技术从其前身 Phi-1.5 扩展 Phi-2。 13 亿参数模型的知识转移加速了训练收敛，从而显着提高了基准分数。</li></ul><h3 class="wp-block-heading">绩效评估</h3><p>Phi-2 经过了各种基准的严格评估，包括 Big Bench Hard、常识推理、语言理解、数学和编码。</p><p> Phi-2 仅拥有 27 亿个参数，其性能优于更大的模型（包括 Mistral 和 Llama-2），并且与 Google 最近发布的 Gemini Nano 2 相匹配或优于： </p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1024" height="568" src="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/microsoft-phi-2-model-benchmark-comparison-ai-artificial-intelligence-1024x568.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-14070" srcset="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/microsoft-phi-2-model-benchmark-comparison-ai-artificial-intelligence-1024x568.jpg 1024w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/microsoft-phi-2-model-benchmark-comparison-ai-artificial-intelligence-300x166.jpg 300w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/microsoft-phi-2-model-benchmark-comparison-ai-artificial-intelligence-768x426.jpg 768w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/microsoft-phi-2-model-benchmark-comparison-ai-artificial-intelligence-1536x852.jpg 1536w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/microsoft-phi-2-model-benchmark-comparison-ai-artificial-intelligence-361x200.jpg 361w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/microsoft-phi-2-model-benchmark-comparison-ai-artificial-intelligence-380x211.jpg 380w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/microsoft-phi-2-model-benchmark-comparison-ai-artificial-intelligence-350x194.jpg 350w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/microsoft-phi-2-model-benchmark-comparison-ai-artificial-intelligence-100x55.jpg 100w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/microsoft-phi-2-model-benchmark-comparison-ai-artificial-intelligence-60x33.jpg 60w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/microsoft-phi-2-model-benchmark-comparison-ai-artificial-intelligence.jpg 1648w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure><p>除了基准测试之外，Phi-2 还展示了其在现实场景中的功能。涉及研究界常用提示的测试揭示了 Phi-2 在解决物理问题和纠正学生错误方面的能力，展示了其超出标准评估的多功能性： </p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1024" height="576" src="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/phi-2-physics-problem-example-1024x576.png" alt="" class="wp-image-14071" srcset="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/phi-2-physics-problem-example-1024x576.png 1024w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/phi-2-physics-problem-example-300x169.png 300w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/phi-2-physics-problem-example-768x432.png 768w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/phi-2-physics-problem-example-355x200.png 355w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/phi-2-physics-problem-example-380x214.png 380w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/phi-2-physics-problem-example-350x197.png 350w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/phi-2-physics-problem-example-100x56.png 100w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/phi-2-physics-problem-example-60x34.png 60w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/12/phi-2-physics-problem-example.png 1347w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure><p> Phi-2 是一个基于 Transformer 的模型，具有下一个单词预测目标，使用来自合成数据集和网络数据集的 1.4 万亿个标记进行训练。训练过程在 96 个 A100 GPU 上进行了 14 天，重点是保持高水平的安全性，并声称在毒性和偏差方面超越了开源模型。</p><p>随着 Phi-2 的发布，Microsoft 继续突破较小的基本语言模型所能实现的界限。</p><p> <em>（图片来源：<a href="https://www.microsoft.com/">微软</a>）</em></p><p><strong>另请参阅：</strong> <a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/2023/12/07/ai-big-data-expo-demystifying-ai-seeing-past-hype/"><strong>人工智能与大数据博览会：揭秘人工智能并超越炒作</strong></a></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><a href="https://www.ai-expo.net/"><img decoding="async" width="728" height="90" src="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01.png" alt="" class="wp-image-11874" srcset="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01.png 728w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-300x37.png 300w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-380x47.png 380w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-350x43.png 350w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-100x12.png 100w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-60x7.png 60w" sizes="(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px" /></a></figure><p><strong>想向行业领导者了解更多关于人工智能和大数据的知识吗？</strong>查看在阿姆斯特丹、加利福尼亚州和伦敦举办的<a href="https://www.ai-expo.net/">人工智能与大数据博览会</a>。该综合活动与<a hre